supplementary-material.p: Identities of proteins present in proviral fractions. Data represent the proteins identified in four proviral fractions of S. aureus supernatant by LC-MS/MS. Hits with an overall score of >40 and with more than 2 peptides are shown. Download Table S1, DOCX file, 0.02 MB.
